learning_outcomes.en:
Students:
- acquires a basic ability for self-assessment and problem solving during one's research activity;
- can make an academic presentation;
- is able to transfer one's own knowledge and research;
- obtains knowledge of classical texts and treatments in semiotics and culture theory;
- obtains abilities to carry out academic research;
- is able to present results of one's research field in oral and written form;
- is able to identify and solve occurring problems and topics in one's own research and help colleagues in these activities;
- is able to initiate and take part in academic discussions in one's field of studies, debate and defend  one's statements.

learning_outcomes.et:
üliõpilased:
- omandavad oskuse algatada, kavandada, rakendada ja kriitiliselt hinnata uurimis- ja arendustööd;
- omandavad oskuse identifitseerida ja lahendada enda teadustöös esiletulevaid probleeme, aidata kolleegidel probleeme identifitseerida ja lahendada;
- omandavad oskuse arutleda ja argumenteerida erialastel teemadel;
- omandavad oskuse oma valdkonna probleeme ja uurimistöö tulemusi esitada suuliselt ja kirjalikult artikli vormis;
- omandavad oskuse oma teadmisi edasi anda;
- omandavad teadmisi semiootika ja kultuuriteooria klassikalistest tekstidest ja teemadest;
- omandavad oskuse läbi viia akadeemilisi uurimusi.
